  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1124">
<l>vāḻta luyirkkaṉṉa ḷāyiḻai cātal </l>
<l>ataṟkaṉṉaḷ nīṅku miṭattu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My fair-jewelled one resembles the living soul (when she is in union with me), the dying soul when she leaves me.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
